Cell["\<\
We now repeat this experiment 1,000 times. How many times do we win in each \
of the experiments?\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.94781588756474*^9, 
  3.947815930734717*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4b497599-99a8-4efa-8b01-\
